    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <section class="mt-12 md:mt-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-6 md:mb-8 text-center">Common Questions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
            <details class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
                <summary class="font-bold text-primary cursor-pointer">What industries do you work with?</summary>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3 text-sm">
                    We've delivered projects across distribution, manufacturing, financial services, insurance, apparel, and professional services. Our approach focuses on understanding business processes, not just technical requirements.
                </p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
                <summary class="font-bold text-primary cursor-pointer">What's your typical project timeline?</summary>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3 text-sm">
                    Small automations: 1-2 weeks. Custom Suitelets: 3-6 weeks. Integration pipelines: 4-8 weeks. Timelines depend on complexity, testing requirements, and client availability for feedback.
                </p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
                <summary class="font-bold text-primary cursor-pointer">Do you provide ongoing support?</summary>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3 text-sm">
                    Yes. We offer retainer-based support for ongoing development, troubleshooting, and optimization. We also provide knowledge transfer documentation so you can maintain solutions internally if preferred.
                </p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
                <summary class="font-bold text-primary cursor-pointer">What's your pricing model?</summary>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3 text-sm">
                    Typical projects range from $15K-$40K and take 4-8 weeks. Most pay for themselves in 3-6 months through headcount savings or revenue protection. We offer project-based (fixed scope), retainer (monthly capacity), and hourly consulting. Detailed proposals provided before any commitment.
                </p>
            </details>

            <details class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6">
                <summary class="font-bold text-primary cursor-pointer">Do you work with offshore teams or directly?</summary>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3 text-sm">
                    All development is done directly by our principal consultant. No offshore teams, no handoffs. You work with one person who understands your business and owns the entire solution.
                </p>
            </details>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <section class="mt-8 md:mt-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-primary-dark text-white rounded-lg p-6 md:p-8 text-center">
